title: Documentary-Climate Change-Global Dimming- Please Share.avi
description:
BBC 2 Horizon Documentary on Global Dimming, Global Warming and the threat to the environment.
Even the most pessimistic forecasts of global warming may now have to be drastically revised upwards. That means a temperature rise of 10&deg;C by 2100 could be on the cards, giving the UK a climate like that of North Africa, and rendering many parts of the world uninhabitable. That is unless we act urgently to curb our emissions of greenhouse gases
